## Environment configuration
Open Git Bash
```sh
配置用户名
git config --global user.name "username"//（ "username"是自己的账户名，）
配置邮箱
git config --global user.email "username@email.com"                                    //("username@email.com"注册账号时用的邮箱)
```
Check whether the configuration is OK
```sh
git config --global --list 
```
Then
```sh
ssh-keygen -t rsa
```
Then press enter three times in a row. After that, go to the system disk directory (usually C: \ users \ Acer. SSH)to check whether there is SSH folder generation


![qclAuq.png](https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/03/29/qclAuq.png)

Add the public key (id_rsa. Pub) in SSH folder to GitHub management platform

![qc1BYF.png](https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/03/29/qc1BYF.png)

## Some examples of the basic syntax of Markdown

#### block quote
>this  
>is  
>a  
>block  
>quote  


#### bulleted list
- this
- is
- a
- bulleted
- list

#### numbered list
1. this
2.  is
3.  a
4.  numbered
5.  list

#### table
id|name|age
:-|:-:|-:
01|Alice|18
02|Sherry|20
03|Tom|19

#### bolded text
**this is a word**


#### italicized text 
*this is a word*


#### strikethrough text
~~this is a word~~

#### code
```
int main()
{
    printf("Hello World!");
    return 0;
}
```
